    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Lightweight solids, usually cubical and often of wood, plastic, or similar material, occurring in sets and designed as children's toys.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
